Figure 29. Dorsal view of 
<taxonomicName class="Arachnida" family="Tenuipalpidae" genus="Tenuipalpus" higherTaxonomySource="CoL" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="Tenuipalpus szarvasensis" order="Trombidiformes" pageId="4" pageNumber="103" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="szarvasensis">Tenuipalpus szarvasensis</taxonomicName>
Bozai, 1970, holotype, female.
</paragraph>
